1
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:05,000
A secret photo?

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:05,830
For real?

3
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,540
She stands up to injustice
and faces it head-on.

4
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:11,250
She's as cool
as a superstar.

5
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:13,130
She's the idol of the entire school.

6
00:00:13,130 --> 00:00:14,880
That's Makishima Reika senpai.

7
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,330
You mean that super hot
Shimabara senpai?

8
00:00:16,330 --> 00:00:16,920
Yeah.

9
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:17,750
No way!

10
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:18,580
Impressive, right?

11
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:20,830
But for an ordinary person like me,

12
00:00:20,830 --> 00:00:22,790
our paths will never cross.

13
00:00:24,540 --> 00:00:26,000
Sami, what's wrong?

14
00:00:26,670 --> 00:00:28,000
It's nothing. Really.

15
00:00:28,380 --> 00:00:30,330
If you keep spacing out like that,
you're going to fall.

16
00:00:30,330 --> 00:00:31,830
Huh? I'm not gonna
fall—

17
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,040
Whoa! Ah!

18
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:35,670
Spoke too soon.

19
00:00:38,290 --> 00:00:40,670
Oh? Kaede, it's rare to see you being so nice.

20
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:41,790
Thanks.

21
00:00:42,290 --> 00:00:43,290
Are you okay?

22
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:44,750
Cosmically invincible.

23
00:00:44,830 --> 00:00:45,880
Reika-sama?

24
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,920
What? Cosmic?

25
00:00:48,330 --> 00:00:49,920
No! I'm sorry!

26
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,130
The term 'Cosmically Invincible'...

27
00:00:52,130 --> 00:00:52,790
...refers to Makishima-sama's...

28
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:53,710
greatest, noblest, and purest...

29
00:00:53,710 --> 00:00:54,830
...magnificent spirit.

30
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:56,880
The one who embodies this magnificent spirit,
Makishima Reika-sama,

31
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:58,380
is respectfully addressed as 'Cosmically Invincible
Reika-sama'.

32
00:00:58,380 --> 00:00:59,500
It's a solemn rule.

33
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,750
What am I even saying?!

34
00:01:01,790 --> 00:01:02,790
How interesting.

35
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:04,580
You dropped this.

36
00:01:05,250 --> 00:01:06,250
Thank you so much.
